            </p>
            <p>
                When I'm not designing, you can find me exploring new coffee shops, reading about psychology, 
                or planning my next travel adventure.
            </p>
            
            <div class="contact-links">
                <a href="mailto:hello@anniesommer.com">Email</a>
                <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/anniesommer">LinkedIn</a>
                <a href="https://dribbble.com/anniesommer">Dribbble</a>
                <a href="/resume.pdf">Resume</a>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <footer class="footer">
            <p>© 2024 Annie Sommer. Designed with care and plenty of coffee.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
